## "recover"

``` go
func CalmDown() {
	// Halt the panic.
	panicValue := recover()
	// Print value passed to panic().
	fmt.Println(panicValue)
}

func Socialize() {
	defer fmt.Println("Goodbye!")
	defer CalmDown()
	fmt.Println("Hello!")
	panic("I need to get out of here!")
	// The below code won't be run!
	fmt.Println("Nice weather, eh?")
}
```

## "recover"

Output:

``` go
